definitions.definition: A person (especially a writer ) who lived during the reign of Queen Elizabeth I , monarch of England and Ireland , from 1558 to 1603.
A person who lived during the reign of Queen Elizabeth II , monarch of the United Kingdom , from 1952 to 2022.
